These are Puzzles for 1x6 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x6-Level-1-1::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: fanta, soy-milk, mirinda, tea, milk, juice
1. the person drinking mirinda is on the far right##1
2. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
3. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
4. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
5. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |     1     |       2        |     3     |      4       |   5   |   6    |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | milk | fanta | juice | tea | mirinda |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x6-Level-1-2::.
The people use 6 different means of transport: bike, bus, motorbike, jet-ski, train, roller
1. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
2. the person driving the jet-ski is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the train is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
5. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |   5    |    6    |
| Transport   | jet-ski | bike | motorbike | roller | train | bus |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x6-Level-1-3::.
The people have 6 different hobbies: dancing, woodworking, baking, collecting, writing, photography
1. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
2. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
3. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far left##1
5. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2     |   3    |    4     |       5       |       6       |
| Hobby   | woodworking | baking | writing | dancing | photography | collecting |

